snippet.title: NOISZ STΔRLIVHT Gameplay First Look Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to mobile devices in 2021, a standalone entry in NOISZ's saga featuring rhythm & bullet hell gameplay hybridized for touchscreens.
Play the free prequel VN: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1329110/2ECONDS_TO_STRLIVHT_Forever_My_Diamond/

NOISZ on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/681530/NOISZ/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/noiszgame
